      User UserRepository.getDefault()
      Returns default credentials: email = System.getenv("USER_EMAIL"); password = "12345"; userValue1 = 0; userValue2 = 0.
      User UserRepository.user104UACredentials()
      Returns credentials for 104UA site: email = System.getenv("USER_EMAIL"); password = System.getenv("LOE_SITE_PASSWORD"); userNumber = System.getenv("104UA_SITE_GAS_PRIVATE_INVOICE"); userValue1 = gasMeterValue; userValue2 = 0.
      User UserRepository.userInfoLvivCredentials()
      Returns credentials for InfoLviv site: email = System.getenv("USER_EMAIL"); password = System.getenv("INFO_LVIV_SITE_PASSWORD"); userNumber = System.getenv("INFO_LVIV_SITE_WATER_PRIVATE_INVOICE"); userValue1 = waterMeterValue; userValue2 = 0.
      User UserRepository.userLOECredentials()
      Returns credentials for LOE site: email = System.getenv("USER_EMAIL"); password = System.getenv("LOE_SITE_PASSWORD"); userNumber = System.getenv("LOE_SITE_PRIVATE_INVOICE") - number consumer from URL (https://info.loe.lviv.ua/consumers/{number}/info); userValue1 = electricityDayValue; userValue2 = electricityNightValue.
      User UserRepository.userLOECredentialsOnlyDayValue()
      Returns credentials for LOE site: email = System.getenv("USER_EMAIL"); password = System.getenv("LOE_SITE_PASSWORD"); userNumber = System.getenv("LOE_SITE_PRIVATE_INVOICE") - number consumer from URL (https://info.loe.lviv.ua/consumers/{number}/info); userValue1 = electricityDayValue; userValue2 = -1.
